*Svejedno* mu je šta drugi misle o njemu. (It doesn't matter to him what other people think of him.)

Nije mu bilo *svejedno* što je čuo. (It wasn't indifferent to him what he heard.)

Nije bilo *svejedno* kako će se završiti problem. (It wasn't indifferent how the problem would end.)

*Svejedno* je da li ću izaći ili ne. (It doesn't matter whether I go out or not.)

Njemu je *svejedno* da li će izgubiti posao ili ne. (It doesn't matter to him if he will lose his job or not.)